column1: Topic : Electricity Generation, Consumption and Tariffs
Title  : M890841 - Electricity Generation And Consumption, Annual
Professional, Scientific & Technical, Administration & Support Activities
Data on industries are classified according to the Singapore Standard Industrial Classification 2015.

ELECTRICITY GENERATION - SOURCE: SP POWERASSETS LTD BEFORE 2003, ENERGY MARKET AUTHORITY WEF 2003.  DATA REFLECT THE GROSS GENERATION IN THE SYSTEM.  FROM JAN 2016, DATA HAVE INCORPORATED OUTPUT FROM SOLAR GENERATION.

ELECTRICITY CONSUMPTION - REFERS TO THE TOTAL ELECTRICITY CONSUMPTION BY END USERS, INCLUDING (EMBEDDED) CONSUMPTION BY AUTOPRODUCERS.  FROM JAN 2016, DATA HAVE INCORPORATED CONSUMPTION OF OUTPUT FROM SOLAR GENERATION.
